Martha M. BUCKLIN, Appellant, v. Charles E. MERRILL et al., Appellees. No. 73. Circuit Court of Appeals, Second Circuit. Dec. 4, 1933. William L. Wemple, of New York City (Daniel J. McMahon, of New York City, of counsel), for appellant. Caruthers Ewing, of New York City, for appellees.

Before L. HAND, SWAN,- and CHASE, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

Judgment affirmed.
